# ESGAntall — Next.js + AI Project

## Stack
- Next.js 14 App Router, TypeScript strict
- SCSS Modules (no Tailwind, no CSS-in-JS)
- Anthropic SDK (`@anthropic-ai/sdk`) — server side only
- Fonts: Space Grotesk (UI) + JetBrains Mono (code/labels)

## Atomic Design Structure
```
src/components/
  atoms/      → Button, Input, Badge, Logo, Text
  molecules/  → Card, ChatBubble, NavBar, InputBar
  organisms/  → Hero, ChatPanel, Sidebar
```

Every component folder MUST have exactly 4 files:
- `ComponentName.tsx`
- `ComponentName.module.scss`
- `ComponentName.types.ts`
- `index.ts`

## Brand Colors (always use CSS vars, never hardcode hex)
```
--color-cyan:   #18E0F7   ← primary accent
--color-blue:   #2E7CFF   ← buttons, links
--color-purple: #6B3DFF   ← gradients
--color-light:  #F6F8FF   ← text
--color-dark:   #0A0E17   ← background
```

## Rules
- Dark background ONLY — never white/light bg
- All colors via CSS custom properties from `src/styles/_tokens.scss`
- `'use client'` only when browser APIs or hooks are needed
- Anthropic SDK NEVER imported in client components
- AI logic lives exclusively in `src/ai/`
